items.name: Elva - Project QT
items.description:
Hello to my 68 dashing followers, I am back with one of the girls I got you guys to vote for, but since it was a draw between Elva and Una so I flipped a coin and it landed on Elva first. I will do Una next. I would also like to say that we are in the top 700 creators on civit and top 300 character creators, which is bonkers and I thank everyone for supporting me. Now onto my new creation:

Well im not really sure about this lora, since its making very mixed results, even though I used good and high resolution datasets. This could also be because im rendering on cpu, which would be unfortunate, or it could be because of my poor tagging but I think that would affect how the character looks and not how blurry the generation is. Please do not take the pictures I generated at face value, I hope it generates much better on other peoples hardware, and if it doesnt then please immediately mention it so I can try making it the 3rd time.

Well apart from that, I made sure to tag all her outfits so she can use a few different clothing items. My suggestion to prompt her are the following: elva, crop top/bikini/fur coat/white shirt, fake animal ears, rabbit ears, forehead jewel, navel, shoulders, striped legwear/thighhighs

Thats all for now, Im not sure when I will upload next, I need some downtime since I have other important things to ponder on and deal with, but I wont be gone for long at all. If this lora works for you make sure to rate it and definitely upload some pictures for me to marvel at, and perhaps drop me a follow if you arent yet :).

items.name: ErosMix ( SFW & NSFW )
items.description:
My first experiment with merging models. (combined 34 models). Recipe lower. VAE baked in. My prompts were made with chatgpt by feeding it someone's book on prompting (Recommend this youtube video)

I wanted a good looking model that could do a bit of everything, everything of what I wanted to get (high quality images even with small prompts). The style is: anime semi realistic

- Pros: can do both men and women easy, big breasts, thick/small, fantasy stuff, decent genitalias, did even a dragon pretty decent, tested a few Loras and did alright with them (you gotta test to see if it does fine with ur loras)

- Cons: struggle with sex scenes (unless you're a master at prompting)

My Settings
It should work with your usual settings but here are mine:

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras / Euler a (works with others as well)

  • Size: 512-512 / 512-768 (I tried 1024-512 and still did pretty fine)

  • Clip skip: 2 (did not test clip skip 1 should be alr. ig)

  • Sampling Steps: 20-30 (I use 30 all the time)

  • Hiresfix upscaler: 4x-UltraSharp / R-ESRGAN 4x Anime6B on 2x, steps: 20, denoise 0.5 (should do fine between 0.3-0.7)

  • Cfg scale: 7 (tested up to 15 and was fine)

My Negative prompt: easynegative, badhandv4, lr, beard, curly, veiny, muscular, ((bodybuilder)), facial hair, mustache, lowres, fewer fingers, out of frame, jpeg artifacts, ugly, duplicate, morbid,mutilated, extra fingers, mutated hands, poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn face, mutation, deformed, blurry, dehydrated, bad anatomy, bad proportions, extra limbs, cloned face, disfigured, gross proportions, malformed limbs, missing arms, missing legs, extra arms, extra legs, fused fingers,(speech bubble:1.3),(text:1.3),(logo:1.3),(signature:1.3)

Recipe (left model 70%, right model 30%):

Anyhentai + 1924 = Result1(pruned)

Result1 + abyssorangemix2_hard = Result2

Result2 + akatsukiSoukenV2 = Result3

Result3 + abyssorangemixv2_V2 = Result4

Result4 + amkumix = Result5

Result18 + duchaitenStylelikeme_v15 = Result19

Result19 + eerieorangemix2Hardcore_eerieorangemix2 = Result20

Result20 + envy2dmix = Result21

Result22 + everydayartEda_v5 = Result23

(The way I did this is I got 70 models, I combined and tried and then when I merged got new 70 models, I tested them all at once, I did around 30 examples with all 70 at once and the model that got my highest score to my needs was the winner, for example other models did great at sex, but bad at pubic hair or black skin, others had nice genitalia while others had bad genitalias, others had good background while others had bad backgrounds. RIP around $20 to merge this model on runpod q_q)

items.name: jjjbonnet - Jerome Bonnet's Signature Photography Style
items.description:
"jjjbonnet" is a unique and captivating photography style created by the talented photographer Jerome Bonnet. With a distinct artistic vision, Jerome's work under "jjjbonnet" offers a compelling blend of creativity, storytelling, and visual aesthetics.

Through "jjjbonnet," Jerome captures moments and subjects in a way that transcends ordinary photography. His images evoke emotions, stir curiosity, and paint a vivid picture of the world from his lens. Each photograph is a masterpiece that reflects Jerome's passion for storytelling through visuals.

With meticulous attention to detail and a keen eye for composition, "jjjbonnet" showcases a range of subjects that leave a lasting impression. Whether it's nature's breathtaking landscapes, candid portraits, or thought-provoking abstracts, Jerome's photography style is a testament to his dedication and artistry.

Embracing both natural light and expert lighting techniques, "jjjbonnet" images are imbued with depth, contrast, and a play of shadows, adding an enchanting dimension to his subjects. The interplay of colors and textures further enhances the visual experience, creating captivating narratives within each frame.

As admirers of Jerome Bonnet's work, we are privileged to witness the world through the lens of "jjjbonnet." His photography style not only captures moments frozen in time but also ignites our imagination and connects us to the essence of his subjects.

Explore the world of "jjjbonnet" and embark on a visual journey that celebrates the power and beauty of photography as an art form. Jerome's passion and creativity shine through in every image, making "jjjbonnet" an enriching experience for photography enthusiasts and art aficionados alike.

GSMaleto Photoreal V3


This new checkpoint was created on the basis of merging other known checkpoints.

This model is my first realistic focus fusion production without the need for LoRAs even with simple prompts, however, it works very well with LoRAs models.

Important recommendations:

Recommended settings for good gens (Automatic1111):

·         Sampling Method: DPM++ SDE Karras (DPM2a Karras also it's very good)

·         Sampling Steps: 22 (20~30 is enough)

·         Width: 768 (Quality improves with 1024)

·         Height: 768 (Quality improves with 1024)

·         CFG Scale: 7 (Less than 7 will produce more realistic images, greater than 7 will produce more animated images)

Hires. fix On (optional)

·         Hires. fix On

·         Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+

·         Hires Steps: 10 (or your preference)

·         Denoising Strength: 0.5

·         Upscale: 1.5

Increase the details with the "adetailer" extension, this makes the face more beautiful without "deformations" depending on the applied settings.


You can use LoRA "BetterCocks" to implement more realistic features, although the checkpoint already has this included, but it's not 100% perfect, so to improve, you can use this, I recommend using a power between 0.3 ~ 0.5.

Positive prompts can be added

Realistic, photo, ultra quality, elegant, highly detailed, photograph

You can also use EasyNegative on "negative prompts" in order to get better quality results.

Negative prompts can be used

Watermark, 3D, canvas frame, Text, censored, ((deformed)), ((extra limbs)), extra arms, ((bad anatomy)), ((disfigured)), (((duplicate))), ((bad art)), poorly drawn face, mutated, extra limb, ugly, poorly drawn hands, missing limb, floating limbs, disconnected limbs, disconnected head, malformed hands, long neck, mutated hands and fingers, bad hands, missing fingers, cropped, worst quality, low quality, (((mutation))), mutation, mutated, mutated hands, poorly drawn, huge calf, bad hands, fused hand, missing hand, disappearing arms, disappearing thigh, disappearing calf, disappearing legs, missing fingers, fused fingers, abnormal eye proportion, Abnormal hands, abnormal legs, abnormal feet, abnormal fingers, amputee, pussy, ((girl)), ((women)), ((female))

items.name: Doggystyle face down
items.description:
LoRA trained to generate a doggystyle position where the receiving partner has their face down and ass up. I couldn't find a name for this pose so don't mind the random trigger I used. Note that this is a complex pose and doesn't solve issues inherent to SD. So it may take you more work to get a good image. It took quite a few iterations before I could get to a point that was stable enough.

Please rate and leave a like if you enjoyed it! And be sure to follow to check out the upcoming models.

Note: this model only works with a square aspect ratio (e.g. 512x512). You can increase the width a bit, not the height. It was trained only with images where the male is out of the frame, so if won't be able to generate a portrait aspect ratio. I recommend using hires fix as well.

  • The main tag is the bare minimum that must be in the prompt: top-down bottom-up

  • Useful tag to help the effect: piledriver doggystyle (yeah, I know it's a bit random)

  • Tags related to the view from the back, especially if it's not achieved with just the main tag: from behind, looking back, ass.

  • Tags related to the sexual activity, especially if it's not achieved with just the main tag: sex, sex from behind, penis, testicles, anal, etc.

Additional info

I make these models for fun and for the challenge and release them for free for everyone to enjoy, for non-commercial use (see license). The one thing I ask of you is to provide rating and feedback! That helps me understand where I can improve and helps me stay motivated to produce more content! I accept suggestions or requests here or on Civitai discord server.
